Motormaster keeps on flying towards Condor as he relays the info, " I sent
Cyclonus to lead an attack on Angel Prime for trespassing on our turf. He
took SPeedbreaker, Drag Strip, Scourge, a Bodicon, Triggerhappy, and
Skullgrin. There should be some Predacons there, but I told them not to
fire on them".
